        "created_at": "2025-05-12T06:22:44.018Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I agree that if this works, it would be the only solution, since the signal history can never be transferred via a total data transfer on the OS side and can also not be accessed externally by connecting to a desktop. So if it is worth it to you, the suggested process would be your only option.</p>\n<p>Just be careful when having the phone repaired. Sometimes they reset the phone while doing this and then your history would be lost permanently.</p>\n<p>You should also be aware that merging histories is currently not possible, so you would lose all history on the new phone when attempting a new transfer.</p>",
